reviewText:
Anthony K is a fresh voice speaking on subjects ranging from how to survive in the ghetto (and what to do when you find yourself in a city who hasn't even paved all its own sidewalks) to being a "hood nerd" (technically savvy people living in the hood). His positive, wonderfully shocking attitude transcends genders, ages and social statuses and shows us that even Modesto can have a fresh perspective within it's borders.

Brrrrraaattttttt.
